# Event Service API Test Suite
# Unified HTTP requests for testing the Event Service API
# Use with REST Client plugin in VS Code or similar tools

# =============================================================================
# CONFIGURATION
# =============================================================================

# Base URL - Change this to match your environment
# Local development: http://localhost:8080
# Docker: http://localhost:8080
# Network: http://192.168.1.10:8080
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

# =============================================================================
# HEALTH CHECK
# =============================================================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

# =============================================================================
# EVENT ENDPOINTS
# =============================================================================

### Create Event - Premier League Match
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Premier League: Manchester United vs Liverpool",
  "description": "Classic rivalry match between Manchester United and Liverpool FC at Old Trafford",
  "location": "Old Trafford Stadium, Manchester",
  "start_time": "2024-06-15T15:00:00Z",
  "end_time": "2024-06-15T17:00:00Z",
  "organizer_id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
}

### Create Event - Champions League Final
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

